{"model":"claude-opus-4-5-20251101","id":"msg_bdrk_018d3sDFPmzo57rAqUDPAPHw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to calculate 17 * 23. Let me do this step by step.\n\nI can break this down in a few ways:\n\nMethod 1: Break down 23\n17 * 23 = 17 * (20 + 3)\n= 17 * 20 + 17 * 3\n= 340 + 51\n= 391\n\nLet me verify with another method:\n\nMethod 2: Break down 17\n17 * 23 = (10 + 7) * 23\n= 10 * 23 + 7 * 23\n= 230 + 161\n= 391\n\nBoth methods give 391, so the answer is 391.","signature":""},{"type":"text","text":"# Calculating 17 × 23\n\n## Breaking it down step by step:\n\nI'll split 23 into (20 + 3) to make this easier:\n\n**Step 1:** 17 × 20 = 340\n\n**Step 2:** 17 × 3 = 51\n\n**Step 3:** Add the results: 340 + 51 = **391**\n\n## Verification using another method:\n\nSplit 17 into (10 + 7):\n- 10 × 23 = 230\n- 7 × 23 = 161\n- 230 + 161 = **391** ✓\n\nThe answer is **391**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":55,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":333}}558 2509
